    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Tick 'Full Index Enabled' and then 'Rebuild Index' of the central repository in 'Global Repositories' under <code>Window &gt; Show View &gt; Other &gt; Maven &gt; Maven Repositories</code>, and it should work.</p>\n\n<p>The rebuilding may take a long time depending on the speed of your internet connection, but eventually it works.</p>\n"
